data.description: Welcome home!!! A stunning and well kept 4 - sided brick home with a Full Finished Basement  that will not last long. The exterior features an established, beautifully landscaped yard with a long driveway with good curb appeal, along with an attached two-car garage. The backyard is a private oasis secured by a wrought iron fence with two  screened-in porches on the lower level/upper level. As you enter into the home, a foyer with a striking high ceiling awaits you. Open concept kitchen with Double Wall Ovens, Mahogany Cabinets, Stainless Steel Appliances  with an  oversized granite island overlooking the breakfast area and family room with fireplace main level consists of multiple living and dining spaces as well.2nd Floor guest suite with full bath.Owner's suite with sitting area, expansive walk-in closet, two separate vanities, soaking tub and oversized shower with a master bath that you will not want to leave. This level has  three additional bedrooms with two full baths. The basement is  finished with additional living space, abundant storage, and another full bath.  This home is zoned for the Union Grove cluster, which includes top performing schools in Henry County. It has a pool, and club house and it is one mile from the Elementary school
